The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for summarizing reviews of products and services. The use of syntactic patterns and topic models suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the focus on user-generated content and sentiment analysis could also place the paper under the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
